Upon starting the Application, you will see a view which list all the games. Select TIC and then press start. 

You will be prompted with another window, which will display "TIC" in bold. Start the button to star game.

The game support restart of the game by pressing the space bar. The geam supports randomly changing the color of the
grid  tiles of the game by pressing "ENTER". 

The game also displays the current player and the amount of points each players has.

When you hover over one of the grid tiles, the tile which you are over will change color. You shouldn't have to click on 
the button itself to see the color change.  

The game also support show which tiles have been selected by drawing the X's and O's for each player. The grid panels 
were implemented by making a NxN button matrix. 
